---
import Base from "@layouts/Base.astro";
import SectionBlurb from "@layouts/SectionBlurb.astro";
import Text from "../components/base/text/Text.astro";
import LinkTo from "../components/base/linkTo/LinkTo.astro";
import CurrentCareerPosition from "../components/custom/CurrentCareerPosition.astro";

const pageSubTitle =
  "Just doing my best to be a curious programer, staying on track and baalance the rest of my life";
---

<Base title="Matterholt" subTitle={pageSubTitle}>
  <div class="mainContent_layout" slot="mainContent">
    <div class="indexHero">
      <div class="indexHeroText"></div>
      <div class="indexHeroSub">
        <Text tag="p">
          Be curious, heard that on a podcast and I like the Idea. The sites
          goals is to attempt to capture my curiosities and wrangle my foucus.
          I've got a touch of ADHD, so keeping on track on things is my
          weakness, like 2 sides of a coin it also lets me explore a vast amount
          of subjects.
        </Text>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="indexContent">
      <Text tag="h2">My Career Focus</Text>
      <Text tag="p">
        I am a Full Stack Developer, I have targeted to primary focus on Front
        end development, I have also have experience with back-end technology. I
        enjoy using Python for scripting, scraping, and general programming. A
        versatile contributor who adapts quickly across the stack. A bit of jack
        of all trades
      </Text>

      <div class="indexContent">
        <Text tag="h3">Current Position</Text>
        <CurrentCareerPosition showDetails={false} />
        <div class="linkTo_box">
          <LinkTo type="internal" path="/careers">Positions </LinkTo>
        </div>
      </div>
      <hr />
    </div>
    <div class="indexContent">
      <Text tag="h2">Who I am</Text>
      <Text tag="p">
        I'm a husband to a beautiful wife. Together we raise our 6 children. Yes
        it is crazy but we both embrace it and enjoy the time we have. We live
        out in rural area and have a little homestead. We focus on growing
        organic produce and regenerative practices. I coach my kiddo's soccer
        team. Try to keep every day spicy and enjoy the challenges that pass my
        way.
      </Text>
      <hr />
    </div>
    <SectionBlurb />
  </div>
</Base>
<style>
  .mainContent_layout {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
  }
  .indexHero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: max-content 1fr;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 25px;
  }
  .indexHeroText {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1;
    word-break: none;
    width: max-content;
    --common_textAlign: center;
  }
  .indexContent {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
    margin-top: 25px;
  }
  .indexHeroExternalLinks {
    grid-column: 3;
    grid-row: 1;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }
  .indexHeroSub {
    grid-row: 2;
    grid-column: 1 /4;
    place-self: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .linkTo_box {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  @media screen and (max-width: 790px) {
    .indexHero {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  }
</style>
